column1: Your query : (( TITLE ( "Parkinson*" OR "PD" ) AND TITLE-ABS-KEY ( "sustained" OR "vowel" OR "phonation" OR "voice" OR "speech" ) AND TITLE-ABS-KEY ( "deep learning" OR "DL" OR "machine learning" OR "ML" OR "computer*" ) AND TITLE-ABS-KEY ( "class*" OR "detect*" OR "progno*" OR "diagno*" OR "predict*" OR "early" OR "feature" OR "spectrogram" OR "pre-trained" OR "transfer" ) ) AND PUBYEAR > 2019 AND PUBYEAR < 2026 AND ( LIMIT-TO ( LANGUAGE,"English" ) )  AND ( LIMIT-TO ( DOCTYPE,"re" ) ) )
